# NoteBrain CLI — Crontab Schedule Template (3-Hour Window)
#
# To install this schedule for your current user:
# 1. Open your crontab editor: crontab -e
# 2. Append the line below (adjusting the path to your notebrain binary if needed):

# Run automated incremental vault indexing every 3 hours (at minute 0 past every 3rd hour)
0 */3 * * * /usr/local/bin/notebrain ingest >> ~/.notebrain/ingest.log 2>&1
